    <thetext>From the old bug tracker, the original bug report by Christopher Vella (chrisvella02) - 2012-02-02 06:03:19 PST read:

I&apos;m using Bibletime 2.9.1 on Ubuntu 11.10. This bug is related to the CPDV module version 1.0.1 from the av11 repository.
Opening the module in a new window works fine, but if I close Bibletime and reopen it the text is not longer shown. Furthmore, the book dropdown list shows only the new testament and the apocrypha. No old testament books or deutero-canonical books are shown.
The same happens if I try to change the bible in an already open window.

---

The issue was confirmed by kalemas, who wrote:

i would confirm this issue, RusSynodal module, on win7-64 with BibleTime
2.9.1</thetext>
